Analysis Using pandas_ta\n\nLeverage `pandas_ta` to analyze market trends:\n\n```python\nimport pandas_ta as ta\nimport pandas as pd\n\n# Sample price data\ndf = pd.DataFrame(client.get_historical_klines('BTCUSDT', Client.KLINE_INTERVAL_1HOUR, '1 day ago UTC'))\ndf.columns = ['Time', 'Open', 'High', 'Low', 'Close', 'Volume', 'CloseTime', 'QuoteAssetVolume', 'NumTrades', 'TBBAV', 'TBQAV', 'Ignore']\ndf['Close'] = df['Close'].astype(float)\n\n# Calculate RSI\ndf.ta.rsi(close='Close', length=14, append=True)\nprint(df.tail())\n```\n","metadata":{}}]}